Jon R. Sabes



Mr. Jon R. Sabes is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at GWG Holdings, Inc., Chief Executive Officer at GWG Life LLC and Chief Executive Officer at Opportunity Finance LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Saving Children Building Families, Inc. and The Insurance Studies Institute Co. Mr. Sabes was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by MEDFinance SA, a Member by American Bar Association, a Member by Financial Industry Regulatory Authority, Inc., and a Member by Minnesota State Bar Association. He also served on the board at Kuhlman Co., Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Colorado and a graduate degree from The University of Minnesota Law School.



